                                        to the Creeds of the [...]<lb/> sent you those two
                                        document). loose who [...]<lb/> them from passage) as my
                                        vouchers for [...]<lb/> my reflections I shall be happy to
                                        [...]<lb/> to say that your prospects have become
                                        brig[...]<lb/> my utmost isolated position does not
                                        aff[...]<lb/> of being [?] to you I remain with you[...]</p>
